<plot>It's in the middle of nowhere, a dramatic landscape not unlike a vision of post-apocalypse. Once known as "The American Riviera", it's the biggest thing on the map in California. Here, in the ghost of one of California's premier resort destinations, a motley group of eccentrics, hell-raisers, and visionaries have found home, and a little piece of heaven.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?141792</url></doc>
